**Additional Protections**:
- **Security audit logging**: Separate log stream for potential attack detection
- **Rate limiting on error endpoints**: Prevent error-based enumeration attacks
- **Custom error pages**: Configure web.xml or Spring to serve static error pages for unhandled cases
- **Response header sanitization**: Remove server version headers (Server, X-Powered-By)
- **Content-Type enforcement**: Always return application/json to prevent content sniffing
